This in-line template is placed after external links, which no longer point to a working website or desired destination.

==Usage==
When spotting a broken link, whose current location is not known, place following after it:
 <nowiki>{{dead link}}</nowiki>

==Examples==
 <nowiki>[http://intentionally.broken-link.is/ somewhere] {{dead link}}</nowiki>
[http://intentionally.broken-link.is/ somewhere] {{dead link|nocat= }}

